    <title>Intermittent: unable to copy selected text</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">Firefox intermittently fails to</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.2">* enable "Edit&gt;Copy" on menu,</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.3">* show "Copy" on context menu,</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.4">* or use keyboard short cut ctrl+C, ctrl-Ins</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.5">currently active/focused selected text on a webpage.</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.6">(ie, the HTML text or from form.input or form.textarea)</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">This happens while browsing with more than one tab.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="3">
            <sentence id="3.1">When this happens if we do "Edit &gt; Select All" and then copy 
(ie, by menu, context menu, or keyboard short)
It copies content from another tab, 
ie a tab in same window but not the current tab.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="4">
            <sentence id="4.1">This was happening since long, but now it is happening very often.</sentence>
            <sentence id="4.2">I first assumed it was problem with my old computer.</sentence>
            <sentence id="4.3">But now found this also on a freshly installed firefox on my new computer.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
